hwVoiceAnalogInterfaceMIB.name: hwVoiceAnalogInterfaceMIB
hwVoiceAnalogInterfaceMIB.contactinfo: PLAT Team Huawei 3Com Technologies co.,Ltd. Shang-Di Information Industry Base, Hai-Dian District Beijing P.R. China http://www.huawei-3com.com Zip:100085

hwVoAnalogIfCommonConfigTable.name: hwVoAnalogIfCommonConfigTable
hwVoAnalogIfCommonConfigTable.description: The voice analog interface common configuration table contains information about configuration parameters for analog voice interface.

hwVoAnalogIfCommonConfigEntry.name: hwVoAnalogIfCommonConfigEntry
hwVoAnalogIfCommonConfigEntry.description: An entry in the voice analog interface common configuration table. The entry is automatically created when a analog voice interface hardware is found.

hwVoAnalogIfConfigPortNumber.name: hwVoAnalogIfConfigPortNumber
hwVoAnalogIfConfigPortNumber.description: Index of voice analog interface common config table. It identify the number of the voice port.

hwVoAnalogIfConfigPortType.name: hwVoAnalogIfConfigPortType
hwVoAnalogIfConfigPortType.description: This object expresses the type of the voice analog interfaces. fxs : the type of the voice port is FXS. fxo : the type of the voice port is FXO. em : the type of the voice port is E&M.

hwVoAnaloglfConfigPortImpedance.name: hwVoAnaloglfConfigPortImpedance
hwVoAnaloglfConfigPortImpedance.description: This object expresses the port impedance of voice analog interfaces. impedance600Real : 600 Ohms This impedance is primarily used by FXS. impedanceComplex : 200 Ohms + 680 Ohms || 100nF This impedance is primarily used by FX0 and E&M.

hwVoAnalogIfConfigInitialDigitTimeOut.name: hwVoAnalogIfConfigInitialDigitTimeOut
hwVoAnalogIfConfigInitialDigitTimeOut.description: This object states the longgest time to wait the first input digit from caller side. The default value is 10 seconds.

hwVoAnalogIfConfigInterDigitTimeOut.name: hwVoAnalogIfConfigInterDigitTimeOut
hwVoAnalogIfConfigInterDigitTimeOut.description: This object states the longest time to wait between two input digit from caller side. The default value is 10 seconds.

hwVoAnalogIfConfigCallDisconnect.name: hwVoAnalogIfConfigCallDisconnect
hwVoAnalogIfConfigCallDisconnect.description: This object states the time the system waits for the caller side to hang up after the connect is disable. The default value is 10 seconds.

hwVoAnalogIfFXSConfigTable.name: hwVoAnalogIfFXSConfigTable
hwVoAnalogIfFXSConfigTable.description: The voice analog interface fxs configuration table contains information about configuration parameters for analog fxs voice interface.

hwVoAnalogIfFXSConfigEntry.name: hwVoAnalogIfFXSConfigEntry
hwVoAnalogIfFXSConfigEntry.description: An entry in the voice analog interface fxs configuration table. The entry is automatically created when a analog fxs voice interface hardware is found.

hwVoAnalogIfFXSConfigPortNumber.name: hwVoAnalogIfFXSConfigPortNumber
hwVoAnalogIfFXSConfigPortNumber.description: Index of voice analog interface fxs config table. It identify the number of the fxs voice port.

hwVoAnalogIfFXSConfigStartMode.name: hwVoAnalogIfFXSConfigStartMode
hwVoAnalogIfFXSConfigStartMode.description: This object expresses the signaling type of analog fxs interface. The default value is loopStart.

hwVoAnalogIfFXSTimerTable.name: hwVoAnalogIfFXSTimerTable
hwVoAnalogIfFXSTimerTable.description: The voice analog interface fxs timer table contains information about timer parameters for analog fxs voice interface.

hwVoAnalogIfFXSTimerEntry.name: hwVoAnalogIfFXSTimerEntry
hwVoAnalogIfFXSTimerEntry.description: An entry in the voice analog interface fxs configuration table. The entry is automatically created when a analog fxs voice interface hardware is found.

hwVoAnalogIfFXSTimerPortNumber.name: hwVoAnalogIfFXSTimerPortNumber
hwVoAnalogIfFXSTimerPortNumber.description: Index of voice analog interface fxs timer table. It identify the number of the fxs voice port.

hwVoAnalogIfFXSTimerDtmf.name: hwVoAnalogIfFXSTimerDtmf
hwVoAnalogIfFXSTimerDtmf.description: This object expresses outgoing dtmf digit duration of the analog fxs interface. The default value is 120 milliseconds

hwVoAnalogIfFXSTimerDtmfInterval.name: hwVoAnalogIfFXSTimerDtmfInterval
hwVoAnalogIfFXSTimerDtmfInterval.description: This object expresses outgoing dtmf interval duration of the analog fxs interface. The default value is 120 milliseconds

hwVoAnalogIfFXOConfigTable.name: hwVoAnalogIfFXOConfigTable
hwVoAnalogIfFXOConfigTable.description: The voice analog interface fxo configuration table contains information about configuration parameters for analog fxo voice interface.

hwVoAnalogIfFXOConfigEntry.name: hwVoAnalogIfFXOConfigEntry
hwVoAnalogIfFXOConfigEntry.description: An entry in the voice analog interface fxo configuration table. The entry is automatically created when a analog fxo voice interface hardware is found.

hwVoAnalogIfFXOConfigPortNumber.name: hwVoAnalogIfFXOConfigPortNumber
hwVoAnalogIfFXOConfigPortNumber.description: Index of voice analog interface fxo config table. It identify the number of the fxo voice port.

hwVoAnalogIfFXOConfigStartMode.name: hwVoAnalogIfFXOConfigStartMode
hwVoAnalogIfFXOConfigStartMode.description: This object expresses the signal type of analog fxo interface. The default value is fxoLoopStart.

hwVoAnalogIfFXOConfigAlertNumber.name: hwVoAnalogIfFXOConfigAlertNumber
hwVoAnalogIfFXOConfigAlertNumber.description: This object expresses the number of rings detected before loop being closed. The default value is 2.

hwVoAnalogIfFXOConfigArea.name: hwVoAnalogIfFXOConfigArea
hwVoAnalogIfFXOConfigArea.description: This object expresses the busy tone of analog fxo interface. The default value is europe.

hwVoAnalogIfFXOPreDialDelay.name: hwVoAnalogIfFXOPreDialDelay
hwVoAnalogIfFXOPreDialDelay.description: This object expresses the pre-dial delay of analog fxo interface. The default value is 1 seconds.

hwVoAnaloglfFXOConfigPortImpedance.name: hwVoAnaloglfFXOConfigPortImpedance
hwVoAnaloglfFXOConfigPortImpedance.description: This object expresses the port impedance of FXO interfaces.

hwVoAnalogIfFXOTimerTable.name: hwVoAnalogIfFXOTimerTable
hwVoAnalogIfFXOTimerTable.description: The voice analog interface fxo timer table contains information about timer parameters for analog fxo voice interface.

hwVoAnalogIfFXOTimerEntry.name: hwVoAnalogIfFXOTimerEntry
hwVoAnalogIfFXOTimerEntry.description: An entry in the voice analog interface fxo timer table. The entry is automatically created when a analog fxo voice interface hardware is found.

hwVoAnalogIfFXOTimerPortNumber.name: hwVoAnalogIfFXOTimerPortNumber
hwVoAnalogIfFXOTimerPortNumber.description: Index of voice analog interface fxo timer table. It identify the number of the fxo voice port.

hwVoAnalogIfFXOTimerDtmf.name: hwVoAnalogIfFXOTimerDtmf
hwVoAnalogIfFXOTimerDtmf.description: This object expresses outgoing dtmf digit duration of the analog fxo interface. The default value is 120 milliseconds

hwVoAnalogIfFXOTimerDtmfInterval.name: hwVoAnalogIfFXOTimerDtmfInterval
hwVoAnalogIfFXOTimerDtmfInterval.description: This object expresses outgoing dtmf interval duration of the analog fxo interface. The default value is 120 milliseconds

hwVoAnalogIfEMConfigTable.name: hwVoAnalogIfEMConfigTable
hwVoAnalogIfEMConfigTable.description: The voice analog interface e&m configuration table contains information about configuration parameters for analog e&m voice interface.

hwVoAnalogIfEMConfigEntry.name: hwVoAnalogIfEMConfigEntry
hwVoAnalogIfEMConfigEntry.description: An entry in the voice analog interface e&m configuration table. The entry is automatically created when a analog e&m voice interface hardware is found.

hwVoAnalogIfEMConfigPortNumber.name: hwVoAnalogIfEMConfigPortNumber
hwVoAnalogIfEMConfigPortNumber.description: Index of voice analog interface e&m config table. It identify the number of the e&m voice port.

hwVoAnalogIfEMConfigSignalMode.name: hwVoAnalogIfEMConfigSignalMode
hwVoAnalogIfEMConfigSignalMode.description: This object expresses the signal mode of the analog e&m interfaces. The default value is immediateDial.

hwVoAnalogIfEMConfigPhyParm.name: hwVoAnalogIfEMConfigPhyParm
hwVoAnalogIfEMConfigPhyParm.description: This object expresses the operation of the analog e&m signal. The default value of this object is fourWiresOperation.

hwVoAnalogIfEMConfigPhyType.name: hwVoAnalogIfEMConfigPhyType
hwVoAnalogIfEMConfigPhyType.description: This object expresses the e&m lead signaling type of the analog e&m interface. The default is type5.

hwVoAnalogIfEMConfigTimeoutRinging.name: hwVoAnalogIfEMConfigTimeoutRinging
hwVoAnalogIfEMConfigTimeoutRinging.description: This object expresses the ring timeout of the analog e&m interface. The value of 65535 indicates the timer is approach infinity. The default value of this object is 60 seconds.

hwVoAnalogIfEMConfigTimeoutWaitDigit.name: hwVoAnalogIfEMConfigTimeoutWaitDigit
hwVoAnalogIfEMConfigTimeoutWaitDigit.description: This object expresses the wait digit timeout of the analog e&m interface. The value of 65535 indicates the timer is approach infinity. The default value of this object is 5 seconds.

hwVoAnalogIfEMTimerTable.name: hwVoAnalogIfEMTimerTable
hwVoAnalogIfEMTimerTable.description: The voice analog interface e&m timer table contains information about timer parameters for analog e&m voice interface.

hwVoAnalogIfEMTimerEntry.name: hwVoAnalogIfEMTimerEntry
hwVoAnalogIfEMTimerEntry.description: An entry in the voice analog interface e&m timer table. The entry is automatically created when a analog e&m voice interface hardware is found.

hwVoAnalogIfEMTimerPortNumber.name: hwVoAnalogIfEMTimerPortNumber
hwVoAnalogIfEMTimerPortNumber.description: Index of voice analog interface e&m timer table. It identify the number of the e&m voice port.

hwVoAnalogIfEMTimerDtmf.name: hwVoAnalogIfEMTimerDtmf
hwVoAnalogIfEMTimerDtmf.description: This object expresses outgoing dtmf digit duration of the analog e&m interface. The default value is 120 milliseconds

hwVoAnalogIfEMTimerDtmfInterval.name: hwVoAnalogIfEMTimerDtmfInterval
hwVoAnalogIfEMTimerDtmfInterval.description: This object expresses outgoing dtmf interval duration of the analog e&m interface. The default value is 120 milliseconds

hwVoAnalogIfEMTimerCallInterval.name: hwVoAnalogIfEMTimerCallInterval
hwVoAnalogIfEMTimerCallInterval.description: This object expresses the dureation of call clearing. The default value is 200 milliseconds.

hwVoAnalogIfEMTimerSendWink.name: hwVoAnalogIfEMTimerSendWink
hwVoAnalogIfEMTimerSendWink.description: This object expresses the max time between receiving seizure signal and sending wink signal. This object can olny be used when hwVoAnalogIfEMConfigSignalMode is 'winkStart'. The default value is 500 milliseconds.

hwVoAnalogIfEMTimerWinkRising.name: hwVoAnalogIfEMTimerWinkRising
hwVoAnalogIfEMTimerWinkRising.description: This object expresses the max time between sending seizure signal and receiving wink signal. This object can only be used when hwVoAnalogIfEMConfigSignalMode is 'winkStart'. The default value is 2000 milliseconds.

hwVoAnalogIfEMTimerWinkHold.name: hwVoAnalogIfEMTimerWinkHold
hwVoAnalogIfEMTimerWinkHold.description: This object expresses the max duration for sending wink signal. This object can only be used when hwVoAnalogIfEMConfigSignalMode is 'winkStart'. The default value is 500 milliseconds.

hwVoAnalogIfEMTimerDialoutDelay.name: hwVoAnalogIfEMTimerDialoutDelay
hwVoAnalogIfEMTimerDialoutDelay.description: This object expresses max time sending called digits. This object can only be used when hwVoAnalogIfEMConfigSignalMode is 'immediate'. The default value is 300 milliseconds.

hwVoAnalogIfEMTimerRising.name: hwVoAnalogIfEMTimerRising
hwVoAnalogIfEMTimerRising.description: This object expresses the wait duration between receiveing seizure signal and sending delay signal. This object can only be used when hwVoAnalogIfEMConfigSignalMode is 'delayDial'. The default value is 300 milliseconds.

hwVoAnalogIfEMTimerHold.name: hwVoAnalogIfEMTimerHold
hwVoAnalogIfEMTimerHold.description: This object expresses the max time sending delay signal. This object can only be used when hwVoAnalogIfEMConfigSignalMode is 'delayDial'. The default value is 400 milliseconds.
